name: WHIZDailyNews
0:
”Alexa, what's my Flash Briefing?”
”Alexa, play my Flash Briefing”
skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
des: Get the latest news headlines from southeastern Ohio. W.H.I.Z. has been serving southeastern Ohio since 1939. Now you can add our news headlines to your Alexa flash briefing for free. If you want to know more about what we do or the latest news visit www.whiznews.com.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
